<div id="sidebar">
<ul>
<li>This web page can be used to request a guest wireless account via SMS (standard text messaging rates apply)  for the UIC-Guest wireless system.  Please note that the text message must be sent to a real phone and this system will not work with the Google Voice text messaging system.</li>

<li>All guest accounts created with this page expire in 48 hours after they are created. There is a limit of 5 guest accounts per semester per person (phone).</li>

<li>All persons requesting guest accounts must accept and abide by the <a href="//accc.uic.edu/policy/guest-wireless">UIC Guest Wireless policy</a>.</li>
</ul>

